  <h2>What We Offer</h2>

  <p>At Top Notch, we:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Transform market research and analysis into real business</li>
    <li>Leverage international partner networks for practical execution</li>
    <li>Provide hands-on support from initial phase through sales and market validation</li>
    <li>Offer negotiation, proposal, and contract support in both Japanese and English</li>
    <li>Minimize risk through a small-start approach</li>
  </ul>

  <hr />

  <h2>From Strategy to Execution</h2>

  <p>Following partner development, we remain involved through the stage where the business becomes viable.</p>

  <p>We translate market analysis and strategy into execution. From channel selection and partner development to initial lot planning and pricing strategy, everything is built at a practical level.</p>

  <p>We do not stop at desk-based strategy. We drive business launch through actual sales, negotiation, and execution. Direct engagement with overseas partners is provided when necessary.</p>

  <p>We adopt a small-start approach, validating market response through test marketing and scaling step by step.</p>

  <hr />

  <div class="case-block">
    <h3>Japan Market Entry Support for a Thai Brand</h3>

    <p>In supporting the entry of a Thai brand into the Japanese market, we executed:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Product selection</li>
      <li>Pricing strategy</li>
      <li>Sales channel development</li>
      <li>Utilization of inbound Thai visitor market</li>
      <li>Pop-up store planning</li>
    </ul>

    <p>We designed a unique pathway based on the inbound Thai visitor segment, developing a Japan Premium strategy and driving a business model focused on actual sales.</p>
  </div>

  <hr />

  <h2>Business Development through Global Partnerships</h2>

  <p>Leveraging extensive international business experience and strong relationships with embassies, we support:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Strategic partnerships with overseas brands</li>
    <li>OEM / manufacturing partner sourcing</li>
    <li>Creation of exhibition and business meeting opportunities</li>
    <li>Practical negotiation</li>
  </ul>

  <p>to accelerate business launch and development.</p>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    <p>Top Notch turns strategy into real business.</p>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
